Interface ClusterControllerGrpc.AsyncService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClusterControllerGrpc.ClusterControllerImplBase
    Enclosing class:
    ClusterControllerGrpc
    public static interface ClusterControllerGrpc.AsyncService
     The ClusterControllerService provides methods to manage clusters
 of Compute Engine instances.

                           io.grpc.stub.StreamObserver<com.google.longrunning.Operation> responseObserver)

        default void diagnoseCluster​(DiagnoseClusterRequest request,
